g.text: Represents and interface for Bayesian Filters. These filters are all related to a
System Model, a Measurement Model and a Prior Density reflecting the
subjective belief of the person applying the filter before getting sensor or any
other form of information about the modeled system.
It is also the base class for particle filters, Kalman Filter, etc.
models of the form P(X | x, u), where both u
and x are continuous or discrete.
